title: 2021 WEEK ONE TNF Recap: Cowboys/Bucs
itunes:title: 2021 WEEK ONE TNF Recap: Cowboys/Bucs
description:
We're all together and it's been a while. Cut us a break! What a great way to open the season with such a great game between the Tampa Bay Buccaneers and the Dallas Cowboys. Trust us, if there is one person you don't want to have the ball with 2 minutes left- it's Tom Brady.
